          A community-driven place to discover and share unforgettable campgrounds across Europe.
          Browse real listings, see locations, and add your own spots.
        </p>

        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4">Browse Campgrounds</a>
          <% if (loginUser) { %>
            <a href="/campgrounds/addCamp" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4">Add Campground</a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4">Join Now</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-3 mt-5 text-start">
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <div class="glass-card p-3 p-md-4 h-100">
              <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-2">Find places</h3>
              <p class="mb-0 text-white-50">Discover campgrounds on the map and explore new regions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <div class="glass-card p-3 p-md-4 h-100">
              <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-2">Share your spot</h3>
              <p class="mb-0 text-white-50">Upload photos and help others find beautiful locations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <div class="glass-card p-3 p-md-4 h-100">
              <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-2">Reviews</h3>
              <p class="mb-0 text-white-50">Read real feedback and leave your own review.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

